This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the computer vision (cs.CV) sub-category. Additionally, the paper discusses methods for training GANs and dealing with latent space, which are topics commonly found in the machine learning (cs.LG) and artificial intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also mentions potential areas for future GAN research, which could fall under the neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE) sub-category. Finally, the second part of the paper discusses experiments done on a dataset of images, which could fall under the multimedia (cs.MM) sub-category.
